  "body": "### What is wrong?\r\n\r\nIt doesn't appear that the `HomesteadVM` correctly enforces the `extra_data` requirements for the 10 headers proceeding after the DAO fork block.\r\n\r\n### How can it be fixed\r\n\r\nImplement `HomesteadVM.validate_header` and enforce the extra data is the specified value for the DAO fork conditionally **if** dao support is enabled.\r\n",
